An out-of-band implementation of OStatus and Salmon for Facebook, Twitter,
Wordpress, and others.

Background: http://snarfed.org/2011-07-27_facebook_app_for_ostatus

The tests require the App Engine SDK and python-mox.

IN PROGRESS!

STATE: hooking up dest and rest of properties in FacebookComment in
FacebookPage.poll(). then expanding poll to iterate over dests for each comment
and match against base url.
